<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$cao-zhou-li" href="/people/cao-zhou-li">曹舟力</a>，<strong title="心理咨询师/督导" class="zu-question-my-bio">心理咨询师/督导</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="10">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$yu-huai-19" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/yu-huai-19" class="zg-link" title="宇怀">宇怀</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$e-zi-84" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/e-zi-84" class="zg-link" title="娥子">娥子</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


